            <title><![CDATA[#感冒是否应该硬抗过去#[费解][感冒]普通感冒：普通感冒属于自限性疾病，一般7-14天就会自然好转。其实感冒药只能缓解症状，它既不能预防感冒，也无法治愈感冒；...]]></title>
            <description><![CDATA[<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E6%84%9F%E5%86%92%E6%98%AF%E5%90%A6%E5%BA%94%E8%AF%A5%E7%A1%AC%E6%8A%97%E8%BF%87%E5%8E%BB%23&amp;extparam=%23%E6%84%9F%E5%86%92%E6%98%AF%E5%90%A6%E5%BA%94%E8%AF%A5%E7%A1%AC%E6%8A%97%E8%BF%87%E5%8E%BB%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#感冒是否应该硬抗过去#</span></a><span class="url-icon"><img alt="[费解]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/d_feijie-c1df37ef03.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><br><br><span class="url-icon"><img alt="[感冒]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/d_ganmao-286fc59b6d.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>普通感冒：普通感冒属于自限性疾病，一般7-14天就会自然好转。其实感冒药只能缓解症状，它既不能预防感冒，也无法治愈感冒；<br><br><span class="url-icon"><img alt="[生病]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/d_shengbing-b740fa9852.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>流行感冒：流行感冒是流感病毒引起的急性呼吸道感染，不仅会伴随腹泻呕吐、高烧不退、浑身酸痛等情况，甚至可能会合并发生肺炎、心肌炎、脑膜炎等疾病，所以一定要及时就医，在医生指导下服用药物，别自己瞎吃！<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[奥特曼]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/others/d_aoteman-7ddbc90d1c.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#小卫唠健康#</span></a><a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E6%9D%A5%E8%BE%9F%E8%B0%A3%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E6%9D%A5%E8%BE%9F%E8%B0%A3%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#小卫来辟谣#</span></a>（健康广东）<img style="" src="https://tvax4.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hk1p1mmyzqj20hz0bjq3e.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br>]]></description>
