            <description><![CDATA[【<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[吃惊]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/d_chijing-59b444adb6.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E8%85%B9%E6%B3%BB%E4%BB%A5%E4%B8%BA%E6%98%AF%E8%83%83%E7%97%85%E7%BB%93%E6%9E%9C%E6%98%AF%E5%BF%83%E6%A2%97%23&amp;extparam=%23%E8%85%B9%E6%B3%BB%E4%BB%A5%E4%B8%BA%E6%98%AF%E8%83%83%E7%97%85%E7%BB%93%E6%9E%9C%E6%98%AF%E5%BF%83%E6%A2%97%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#腹泻以为是胃病结果是心梗#</span></a> 】今天是中国第10个“中国心梗救治日”。胸痛、胸闷或伴有背痛、多汗等，这些都可能是心梗的预警信号<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[揣手]" src="https://face.t.sinajs.cn/t4/appstyle/expression/ext/normal/af/2022_chuaishou_org.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>！突发心梗该怎么办？日常哪些习惯会让你伤“心”？如何预防心梗？戳👇🏻<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#小卫唠健康#</span></a>（央视新闻） <img style="" src="https://tvax1.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hk1nh501wcj20go0gowfh.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://tvax1.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hk1nh500kuj20go0goq44.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://tvax1.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hk1nh50d8lj20go0goq3z.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://tvax3.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hk1nh508ejj20go0gomyb.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://tvax1.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hk1nh525s8j20go0got9j.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://tvax4.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hk1nh4zaewj20go0gowfr.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://tvax2.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hk1nh4zz4rj20go0goq3y.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://tvax2.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hk1nh50d29j20go0godgz.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://tvax4.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hk1nh514ynj20go0got9y.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br>]]></description>
